#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:208
msgid "I am Yraec, head of this village. What do you want, orcs?"
msgstr "我叫亞艾克，此村村長。獸人，妳們想幹嘛？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:209
msgid "Erurag sent us. He wants half of your gold. The same conditions as last year."
msgstr "俄如萊格派我們來的。他要收妳們壹半的金幣。跟去年壹樣。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:210
msgid "Last year you took us by surprise. This time we have prepared. Men, to arms!"
msgstr "去年妳們對我們搞突襲，但這回我們可有準備了。夥計們，抄家夥！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:219
msgid "In vain you start it, village head. Now I have to take your head off."
msgstr "這可沒用，村長。我馬上就砍下妳的頭。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:220
msgid "Chief Erurag ordered to not kill him."
msgstr "俄如萊格首領叫我們不要殺他的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:221
