msgstr "首領以為他們會給咱更好的接待，但這是他們逼我們的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:222
msgid "I will share with you one important military wisdom - obey the orders. Now you are young, but you will get it later."
msgstr "我得告訴妳壹個重要的兵法——將在外，君命有所不受。現在妳還小，不過妳以後會懂的。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:223
msgid "Hm ... Village head, I'll tell you what will happen now. We will defeat all your archers. We will defeat all your horsemen. Also, we will defeat any civilian who will make a miserable attempt to attack us. After that you will either give us the gold or I'll take it by force along with your head. I will make a good cup out of it. I prefer the second option, but you will have a chance to decide."
msgstr ""
"哼嗯…村長，我跟妳說我們現在要幹啥。我們要斬盡妳們所有的弓箭手，殺絕妳們壹切的騎師，還有所有想惹我們的卑賤小民。事後要麽妳給錢，要麽我拿錢還有妳的頭！我還會用它做個好杯子。我喜歡第二條，妳也有機會再考慮考慮。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\02_the_tribute.cfg:224
msgid "I will not listen to this pitiful orc. Men, protect our village. Death to the orcs!"
msgstr "我才不會聽這個可憐的獸人胡扯！夥計們，保護村子，殺了獸人！"

#. [event]
