#. [else]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:859
msgid "Draw. Final score $erurag_score|:$grolo_score|"
msgstr "平局，最終分數是Final score $erurag_score|:$grolo_score|。"

#. [else]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\05_the_competition.cfg:860
