#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:593
msgid "Death of Bart (the wolf)"
msgstr "巴特（狼）死亡"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:754
msgid "Campfire Fake Unit"
msgstr "營火假單位"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:778
msgid "Bogarg, what is going on here?"
msgstr "博伽格，怎麽回事？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:779
msgid "No time to talk, we must hurry. Water is flooding the cave!"
msgstr "沒時間解釋了，我們得趕緊。水要漫到洞穴裏了！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:785
msgid "Find the exit"
msgstr "找到出口"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1006
msgid "Hurry up!"
msgstr "快點！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1012
msgid "Move Rark, Bart and Bogarg into the Nessa's room"
msgstr "移動拉克、巴特和博伽格到奈薩的房間裏"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1016
msgid "Nessa must be inside her room"
msgstr "奈薩必須在房間裏面"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1062
msgid "Rark, it's time to open the door and see what's behind it."
msgstr "拉克，是時候開門看看門後面是什麽了。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1094
msgid "Move Rark to the door"
msgstr "移動拉克到門旁"

#. [label]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1135
msgid "The Great Tree"
msgstr "參天大樹"

#. [event]: id=open_cave_door
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1152
msgid "I can't."
msgstr "我不行。"

#. [event]: id=open_cave_door
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1153
msgid "Believe me, you are the only one who can open it."
msgstr "相信我，妳是唯壹能開這個門的。"

#. [event]: id=open_cave_door
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1209
msgid "Ha - ha!"
msgstr "哈—哈！"

#. [event]: id=open_cave_door
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1210
msgid "What does that mean?"
msgstr "這是什麽意思？"

#. [objectives]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1214
msgid ""
"This scenario is Rark's nightmare\n"
"\n"
"Each turn death spreads across the forest. Defeat the enemy leader before the Great Tree near your castle dies."
msgstr ""
"這壹幕是拉克的噩夢\n"
"\n"
"死亡每回合都會在森林裏蔓延。在妳城堡旁的參天大樹死亡前殺了敵方首領。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1218
msgid "Defeat the enemy leader"
msgstr "殺了敵方首領"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1222
msgid "Death of the Great Tree"
msgstr "參天大樹死亡"

#. [note]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1242
msgid "Rark can recruit now."
msgstr "拉克可以征募了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1300
msgid "I feel a black power coming from the enemy castle. It kills the forest."
msgstr "我感受到來自敵人城堡的黑暗力量，它在殺死森林。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1467
msgid "The Great Tree died."
msgstr "參天大樹死了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\07_escaping_the_nightmare.cfg:1478
msgid "Finally it's over!"
msgstr "總算是完了！"

#. [scenario]: id=08_the_time_has_come
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:6
msgid "The Time Has Come"
msgstr "是時候了"

#. [objectives]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:87
msgid ""
"All recalled units will go with you.\n"
"The rest of the recall list will stay with Erurag."
msgstr ""
"所有被召回的單位都會跟妳走。\n"
"剩下的單位會留在俄如萊格那兒。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:90
msgid "Recall units you want to take with you"
msgstr "召回妳想帶走的單位"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:94
msgid "End turn"
msgstr "結束回合"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:237
msgid "Erurag, thank you for all you have done for me. The time has come. I have to find the murderer of my parents and avenge all of my tribe."
msgstr "俄如萊格，謝謝妳為我做的壹切。時間到了。我必須要去找到我父母的兇手，為我的整個部落報仇。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:238
msgid "I understand, you are a ready. You must understand me too, I cannot send all my veterans with you."
msgstr "我理解，妳已經準備好了。我沒法派所有的老兵跟妳去，妳也得理解我。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:239
msgid "I am going with you, Rark."
msgstr "我跟妳走，拉克。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:240
msgid "And I will join you, my friend."
msgstr "我也加入妳，好夥計。"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:246
msgid "Me too. What about you, Merudda?"
msgstr "我也是。麽魯達，妳呢？"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:247
msgid "Of course I will go with you, if you will pay me."
msgstr "只要妳付我錢，我當然會跟妳走。"

#. [then]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:255
msgid "Recall Merudda if you want her to join your party."
msgstr "如果妳想麽魯達加入妳的隊伍，就召回她。"

#. [else]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:258
msgid "Me too."
msgstr "我也是。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:265
msgid "The wolves are loyal to us."
msgstr "那些狼都忠誠於我們。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:266
msgid "It's time to prepare for the journey."
msgstr "是時候準備上路了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:272
msgid "Good hunting, Rark! I would be happy if you return to my tribe when you are done. Or will you lead your own tribe?"
msgstr "祝妳獵殺成功，拉克！當妳辦完事兒後我歡迎妳回到我的部落。或者妳會領導自己的部落嗎？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:273
msgid "We'll see. Bart, show the way."
msgstr "以後再說。巴特，帶路吧。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\08_the_time_has_come.cfg:274
msgid "With pleasure."
msgstr "是！"

#. [scenario]: id=09_a_friend_of_my_enemy
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\09_a_friend_of_my_enemy.cfg:6
msgid "A Friend of My Enemy"
msgstr "敵人的朋友"

#. [side]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\09_a_friend_of_my_enemy.cfg:48
msgid "Alliance"
msgstr "聯盟"

#. [unit]: type=Fugitive, type=Outlaw, id=alliance_leader
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\09_a_friend_of_my_enemy.cfg:69
msgid "Vaella"
msgstr "外拉"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\09_a_friend_of_my_enemy.cfg:130
msgid "Defeat Vaella"
msgstr "殺了外拉"

#. [note]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\09_a_friend_of_my_enemy.cfg:151
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:283
msgid "In this scenario each village provides 2 income gold. Village upkeep support is 1 unit level as usual."
msgstr "在這壹關裏每個村子提供2枚金幣的收入，村子提供的維護費用照常為1。"

#. [note]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\09_a_friend_of_my_enemy.cfg:154
msgid "Enemy units will not move out of their villages."
msgstr "敵人不會離開村子。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\09_a_friend_of_my_enemy.cfg:175
msgid "Hi there, dwarves and outlaws. Do you know Uritbor? I have a message for him."
msgstr "嗨，那邊的矮人們和混子們。妳們認識厄瑞特博不？我有信給他。"

#. [event]
