#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:804
msgid "You got what you deserve, dwarvish king. Blood for blood."
msgstr "矮人國亡，這是妳的報應！血債血償！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:805
msgid "We made it! Victory is ours!"
msgstr "我們贏了！我們勝利了！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:806
msgid "The king is dead. Retreat!"
msgstr "國王死了，撤！"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:810
msgid "Trolls and orcs friends, smashed dwarves."
msgstr "巨魔和獸人，朋友，砸碎矮人"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:825
msgid "My parents are avenged, they will find eternal rest. I feel tremendous relief."
msgstr "我爹娘的仇報了，他們能永遠安息了。我感到重擔卸下了。"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:826
msgid "What will we do next?"
msgstr "我們接下來要幹啥？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:827
msgid "I don't know yet. No need to hurry. Can you hear it?"
msgstr "我還不知道，先別急，妳能聽見嗎？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:828
msgid "Hear what?"
msgstr "聽見啥？"

#. [event]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\scenarios\13_blood_for_blood.cfg:829
msgid "The silence at the end."
msgstr "我苦苦期盼的平靜。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Cannon, race=mechanical
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Cannon.cfg:119
msgid "Dwarvish Cannon"
msgstr "矮人大炮"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Cannon, race=mechanical
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Cannon.cfg:130
msgid "Cannon is one of the most advanced and deadly weapons. Dwarvish engineers keep the technology of manufacturing this weapon in strict confidence. Cannon shoots at a long distance and causes great damage to both living targets and buildings. No living creature, with the exception of the most enduring and invincible monsters, can survive after a projectile hit."
msgstr "大炮是最先進又致命的武器之壹。矮人工程師們嚴格保守著生產這種武器的工藝。大炮射程很長而且能慘重打擊活目標和建築物。沒有生物能在壹炮之下還活著，即使是最強硬最無敵的怪物。"

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Cannon.cfg:134
msgid "cannon^missile"
msgstr "導彈"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Cart, race=mechanical
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Cart.cfg:5
msgid "Dwarvish Cart"
msgstr "矮人鬥車"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Cart, race=mechanical
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Cart.cfg:16
msgid "This cart is used to transport mined minerals."
msgstr "這輛鬥車被用來運輸采集的礦物"

#. [variation]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Cart.cfg:43
msgid "empty"
msgstr "空車"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish King, race=dwarf
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_King.cfg:5
msgid "Dwarvish King"
msgstr "矮人國王"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish King, race=dwarf
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_King.cfg:18
msgid "Clad in shining armor, these dwarves are kings from under the mountains. They wield axe and hammer with masterful skill, and can hit a target with a thrown hand axe at several paces. Though slow on their feet, these dwarves are a testament to the prowess of their kin."
msgstr "這些穿著閃亮鎧甲的矮人是山下的國王。他們揮舞斧和錘有大師的水平，還能在幾步外扔壹個手斧打擊目標。即使腳慢，這些矮人仍是他們家族勇猛的證明。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Miner, race=dwarf
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Miner"
msgstr "矮人礦工"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Miner, race=dwarf
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:18
msgid "Dwarvish miners are the grunt workers of Dwarvish society. They take the precious ores out of the ground, but do not ever take part in the crafting of weapons or artifacts."
msgstr "矮人礦工是矮人社會的下層工人。他們從土地裏挖出寶貴的礦石，但從來不參與制作武器或手工藝品。"

#. [attack]: type=pierce
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:21
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:30
msgid "pick"
msgstr "鑿"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Torchbearer, race=dwarf
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Torchbearer.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Torchbearer"
msgstr "矮人火炬手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Dwarvish Torchbearer, race=dwarf
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Dwarvish_Torchbearer.cfg:19
msgid "Dwarvish torchbearer usually join expeditions to the deepest and darkest reaches of the underground, helping other dwarves in finding their way and dazzling dangerous creatures not used to the light."
msgstr "矮人火炬手常常加入探險隊到最深最黑的地下，幫其他矮人探路並照暈不習慣光亮的危險生物。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Goblin Piercer, race=goblin
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Goblin_Piercer.cfg:5
msgid "Goblin Piercer"
msgstr "地精長槍兵"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Goblin Piercer, race=goblin
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Goblin_Piercer.cfg:24
msgid "Goblins are used by the orcs as skirmishers to disrupt the enemy's battle line. Those who manage to survive their first few battles equip themselves with a long spear to compensate for their short reach, and better armor to guard their diminuitive frames."
msgstr "地精被獸人用作遊擊戰士來破壞敵人的戰線。這些在之前的戰鬥中活下來的地精為自己裝備了長槍來彌補自己的短處，還有更好的鎧甲保護他們的小身子。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Goblin Raider, race=wolf
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Goblin_Raider.cfg:5
msgid "Goblin Raider"
msgstr "地精襲擊手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Goblin Trumpeter, race=goblin
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Goblin_Trumpeter.cfg:5
msgid "Goblin Trumpeter"
msgstr "地精號令手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Goblin Trumpeter, race=goblin
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Goblin_Trumpeter.cfg:24
msgid "Only the best of rousers can hope to become a trumpeter. Trumpeters spend many hours studying the subtleties of the complex orc war signals. For the orcs, such signals are much more than a simple message of advance or retreat, they inspire their entire army and reinforce their bloodthirsty nature. Many orc warlords consider their trumpeter a trusted confidante and sometimes a trumpeter may be allowed to consult with the warlord on his battle plan."
msgstr "只有最好的煽動者才有可能成為號令手。號令手花了很多小時學習復雜的獸人戰爭信號的細節。對於獸人來說，這樣的信號比簡單的前進或撤退信息含義更豐富。他們鼓舞整個軍隊並增強他們天生好戰的本性。很多獸人軍閥將他們的號令手視為值得信賴的人，有時候號令手會被允許與軍閥壹起商討戰鬥計劃。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Earth Golem
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Golems.cfg:7
msgid "Earth Golem"
msgstr "地粘土怪"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Stone Golem, race=monster
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Golems.cfg:51
msgid "Stone Golem"
msgstr "石人"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Stone Golem, race=monster
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Golems.cfg:64
msgid "Larger than most men and with a skin of stone, the Stone Golems are bulwarks in battle. They are carved out from the mountains and animated by skillful mages."
msgstr "石皮膚，比大多人類大，石人是戰鬥中的活堡壘。他們被強大的法師從山裏鑿出來並賦予行動能力。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Rock Golem, race=monster
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Golems.cfg:112
msgid "Rock Golem"
msgstr "石巨人"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Rock Golem, race=monster
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Golems.cfg:126
msgid "Over time the Golems take on mass and size by merging with other rocks. Rock Golems hit hard and withstand tremendous amount of damage."
msgstr "隨著時間的推移，石人通過合並其他石頭來增加數量和大小。石巨人能抵擋大量傷害，打得還狠。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Mercenary, race=human
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Human_Mercenary.cfg:5
msgid "female^Mercenary"
msgstr "雇傭兵"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Mercenary, race=human
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Human_Mercenary.cfg:19
msgid "Veteran mercenaries become notorious for both their ruthlessness and ability to elude capture. They can be dangerous in their element, though no match for the sheer numbers that law-abiding soldiery can throw at them."
msgstr "因為他們的殘忍和逃避追捕的能力，這些老練的犯罪分子惡名昭彰。當組成小團體時他們很危險，但是這顯然無法和守法的軍隊所能派遣來對付他們的士兵數量相比。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Outcast, race=human
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Human_Outcast.cfg:5
msgid "female^Outcast"
msgstr "流放者"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Outcast, race=human
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Human_Outcast.cfg:18
msgid "After some years of service, former ‘footpads’ rise up in the ranks of their fellow outcasts. Having proven themselves in combat, they are given more dangerous tasks, and a greater share of the spoils. Though many opponents would mock their choice of weaponry, the outcasts are well aware of its deadly capacity, and also of the ready availability of ammunition. Outcasts are somewhat ill at ease fighting during the day, preferring the cover of nightfall."
msgstr "為團夥效力多年後，從前的“走卒”在同夥中的地位有所提升。他們已經證明了自己在戰鬥中的價值，所以被委以更加危險的任務，並能分到更大比例的贓物。雖然許多對手嘲笑他們的武器，他們自己卻很清楚它們的致命威力，同時也深知其彈藥來源相當廣泛。大白天作戰讓遊寇有點兒不適應，他們還是喜歡在夜幕掩護之下行動。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Magic Wall, race=mechanical
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Magic_Wall.cfg:18
msgid "This is a very strong magic wall. It is practically indestructible by usual weapons. Each turn it regenerates 8 HP."
msgstr "這是壹堵非常強硬的魔法墻。使用常規武器幾乎不能摧毀它。每回合它會自愈8點生命值。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Naga Archer, race=naga
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Naga_Archer.cfg:4
msgid "Naga Archer"
msgstr "娜迦弓箭手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Naga Archer, race=naga
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Naga_Archer.cfg:19
msgid "Although the main weapon of nagas is sword, there are those who show more ability to archery. Naga Archer not only provides support for swordsmen, but can also defeat the enemy, especially those who do not have ranged weapons with them."
msgstr "雖然娜迦的主要武器是劍，但也有壹些在射術上展現出更多才能的娜迦。娜迦弓箭手不僅為娜迦劍士提供支援，也能擊敗敵人，尤其是對沒有遠程攻擊武器的敵人來說。"

#. [female]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Naga_Archer.cfg:22
msgid "Nagini Archer"
msgstr "娜迦弓箭手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Naga Marksman, race=naga
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Naga_Marksman.cfg:4
msgid "Naga Marksman"
msgstr "娜迦神射手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Naga Marksman, race=naga
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Naga_Marksman.cfg:20
msgid "Naga Archers who show more mastery and accuracy with their bows are promoted to the ranks of the Marksman. They are more skilled with their bows and can shoot down anything that is foolish enough to enter their domains."
msgstr "在弓箭上展現出更多才能且更精準的娜迦弓箭手會提升成為神射手。他們能更熟練地使用弓箭並且能射倒任何蠢到進入他們領地的東西。"

#. [female]
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Naga_Marksman.cfg:27
msgid "Nagini Marksman"
msgstr "娜迦弓箭手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Avenger, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Avenger.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Avenger"
msgstr "獸人報仇者"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Avenger, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Avenger.cfg:19
msgid "When its hard to remember all the victims of Orcish Tracker, orcs give it a new name - Orcish Avenger. Orcish Avenger is a very dangerous and versatile fighter who perfectly masters both sword and crossbow. In battle, it uses all means for the quickest and most effective killing of the enemy. If Orcish Avenger chose life not among the wild nature, but among the orcs, rumors of its combat exploits are already widely known. Orcish Avenger gains high prestige among orcs and can lead an orcish tribe."
msgstr "當獸人追獵者的受害者數不清的時候，獸人們會給他壹個新名稱——獸人報仇者。獸人報仇者是壹種非常危險又多才能的戰士，同時完美精通弩和劍。在戰鬥中，他盡壹切辦法用最快最有效的方法殺掉敵人。如果獸人報仇者選擇非野外而是在獸人之間的生活，他的作戰功績會廣為流傳。獸人報仇者在獸人之間贏得了很高的聲譽，而且能領導獸人部落。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Hunter, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Hunter.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Hunter"
msgstr "獸人獵手"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Hunter, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Hunter.cfg:16
msgid "Hunting is the main way to feed an orcish tribe. Orcish Hunters successfully mastered this craft. Orcish Hunters usually are not present in the battlefield, however they may compete with Orcish Archers. Moreover, Orcish Hunter is a marksman and has better skills at hitting moving targets. Orcish Hunter needs to fight wildlife and survive in difficult conditions, with the result that its vitality is relatively high."
msgstr "打獵是獸人部落主要的食物來源。獸人獵手成功地掌控了這壹技能。獸人獵手們不常出現在戰場上，然而他們能比得上獸人弓箭手。還有，獸人獵手是神射手並有更棒的攻擊移動目標的技巧。獸人獵手需要與野生動物作戰並在困難的處境下生存，於是這造就了他們相對較高的活力。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Novice Shaman, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Novice_Shaman.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Novice Shaman"
msgstr "獸人新手薩滿"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Novice Shaman, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Novice_Shaman.cfg:16
msgid "Orcish Shamans are the guardians of orcish magic. Respected among orcish tribes, they form the Orcish Council, which makes important decisions for the whole Orcish community and arbitrates the many conflicts that arise between tribes of this argumentative race. Although physically weak (for Orcs), Orcish Shamans are good spell casters and can curse their enemies, draining their life. Novice Shamans are still young and vigorous, but their spell-casting ability still needs improvement."
msgstr "獸人薩滿是獸族魔法的守衛者，受到各部落的尊重。他們建立的長老會仲裁獸人團體間的糾紛。盡管他們身體脆弱（對於獸人而言），薩滿卻是魔咒專家──通過詛咒敵人，吸取他們的生命。這些年輕人精力旺盛，但魔力尚需鍛練。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Ranger, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Ranger.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Ranger"
msgstr "獸人遊俠"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Ranger, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Ranger.cfg:16
msgid "A certain time must pass before the Orcish hunter can become an Orcish Ranger. Not always Oricsh Ranger is fighting with wildlife, sometimes it has to clash with humans, elves, dwarves and other races inhabiting Wesnoth. Because of that, its sword skill has increased. As the main weapon, it replaced the primitive orcish bow with a more complex and dangerous crossbow."
msgstr "獸人獵手要成為獸人遊俠必須經過壹定的時間。獸人遊俠並不總是跟野生動物戰鬥，有時候他不得不與人類、精靈、矮人和其他住在韋諾的生物起沖突。因此，他的劍術提升了。作為主要的武器，原始的獸人弓被替換成了壹把更復雜更強大的十字弩。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Shaman, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Shaman.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Shaman"
msgstr "獸人薩滿"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Shaman, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Shaman.cfg:16
msgid "Orcish Shamans are the guardians of orcish magic. Respected among orcish tribes, they form the Orcish Council, which makes important decisions for the whole Orcish community and arbitrates the many conflicts that arise between tribes of this argumentative race. Although physically weak (for Orcs), Orcish Shamans are good spell casters and can curse their enemies, draining their life."
msgstr "獸人薩滿是獸族魔法的守衛者，受到各部落的尊重。他們建立的長老會仲裁獸人團體間的糾紛。盡管他們身體脆弱（對於獸人而言），薩滿卻是魔咒專家──通過詛咒敵人，吸取他們的生命。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Tracker, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Tracker.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Tracker"
msgstr "獸人追獵者"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Tracker, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Tracker.cfg:16
msgid "Orcish Trackers tend to live a recluse life. They can live in a wild on their own, track down animals or trap them. Even one Orcish Tracker may defeat a small group of untrained bandits. Thus, they do not need to adhere to any particular orcish tribe. Although, any orcish leader will be happy to have Orcish Tracker in their ranks, and for a fee Orcish Tracker can provide their services on the battlefield. First of all, Orcish Tracker got its name for its ability to track down wild animals, but in addition it has a second meaning. Orcish Tracker often gets the task to track down and eliminate an important target in the camp of the enemy."
msgstr "獸人追獵者傾向於過隱居的生活。他們可以獨自在野外生活，追蹤動物或用陷阱抓住他們。甚至壹個獸人追獵者都有可能打敗壹小組沒訓練的強盜。因此，他們不需要依靠任何的獸人部落。即使如此，任何獸人首領都喜歡擁有獸人追獵者的頭銜，給些錢的話，獸人追獵者還可以在戰場上效力。首先，獸人追獵者得到這個頭銜是因為追蹤野生動物的能力，但它還有另外壹個意義，獸人追獵者常常收到追蹤並消滅敵人營地裏重要目標的任務。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Warlock, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Warlock.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Warlock"
msgstr "獸人魔法大師"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Warlock, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Warlock.cfg:17
msgid "Orcish Shaman who decided to improve battle spells is known as Orcish Warlock. Orcish Warlock still can heal wounded comrades, however its main specialization is a magical spell. This spell has a high chance to hit an enemy and deal significant damage. Since Oricsh Warlock drains the life energy from its victims, it can effectively heal itself and kill the enemy at the same time. In hands of a wise leader, Orcish Warlock can cause a lot of troubles to its enemies."
msgstr "決定提升戰鬥魔法的獸人薩滿被譽為獸人魔法大師。獸人魔法大師也能治療受戰傷的戰友，然而他的主要專長是魔咒。這種魔咒有很高的幾率命中敵人並且造成可觀的傷害。因為獸人魔法大師能吸取敵人的生命能量，他可以有效地在治療自身的同時殺掉敵人。在壹個精明的首領手下，獸人魔法大師能為敵人造成很多麻煩。"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Witchdoctor, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Witchdoctor.cfg:4
msgid "Orcish Witchdoctor"
msgstr "獸人巫醫"

#. [unit_type]: id=cban Orcish Witchdoctor, race=orc
#: Captured_by_a_Nightmare\units\Orcish_Witchdoctor.cfg:18
msgid "Orcish Shaman who decided to improve healing skills is known as Orcish Witchdoctor. Orcish Witchdoctor can quickly heal even heavily wounded comrades. A wise orcish warchief tries to get Orcish Witchdoctor under its command, since it is hard to underestimate the healers support on the battlefield. Even the warchief has higher chances to survive the battle, if it has a capable healer on its side."
msgstr "決定提升治療能力的獸人薩滿被譽為獸人巫醫。獸人巫醫能快速為受重傷的兄弟療傷。精明的獸人戰爭領袖會嘗試得到獸人巫醫到其旗下，因為戰場上醫療兵的作用很難被輕視。如果有個能幹的醫療兵在身邊的話，甚至戰爭首領都更容易在戰鬥中活下來。"

