msgid "Each Drake Slave produces 2 gold per turn. When drakes start their turn, Drake Slave may escape and move under their side. If Drake Slave has no adjacent guardians, it will escape. if it has only one adjacent guardian, it has 30% chance to escape. If it has two adjacent guardians, it has 10% chance to escape. if it has more than two adjacent guardians, it can't escape. If Drake Slave has escaped, attack it to move it back under your control."
msgstr "每個龍人奴隸每回合產生2金幣。當龍人的回合開始時，龍人奴隸可能會逃跑並回到他們那邊。如果龍人奴隸沒有臨近的監管，他會逃跑。如果只有壹個臨近的監管，他逃跑的概率是30%。如果有兩個臨近的監管，他逃跑的概率是10%。如果他有兩個以上的監管，他無法逃跑。如果龍人奴隸逃跑了，攻擊他能讓他重歸妳控制。"

